  "slug": "harvest-scythes",
  "title": "Harvest Scythes",
  "description": "Harvest crops in an area",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><strong>Harvest Scythes</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Harvest crops in a range</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Right clicking with a scythe will harvest (and replant) nearby crops in a certain range based on the tool, if those crops are fully grown.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Right clicking on dirt/grass turns it into farmland like a normal hoe.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Some scythes will harvest in a circular shape, whilst others will harvest in a square shape, based on their tier.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Example of circle-shape harvest:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 280px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/316/261/javaw_osdmgc6zs5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"491\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">General recipe, using different ingots for different tools:</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 390px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/316/257/javaw_zxhy73vuug.png\" alt=\"General Crafting Recipe\" width=\"341\" height=\"161\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 390px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">There is also a scythe-only enchant \"Crop Reaper\" that increases their range.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">As of 2.0.0, this mod also adds machetes, which will break surrounding leaf blocks depending on the tool.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The general recipe for the machetes:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 360px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/361/124/macrec.png\" width=\"341\" height=\"171\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 390px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Currently supporting tool materials from the following mods:</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/astromine-foundations\">Astromine Foundations</a> (1.16.5)</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/more-gems-fabric\">More Gems [Fabric]</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/hellish-materials\">Hellish Materials</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/betternether\">Better Nether</a> (1.16.5)</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/betterend\">Better End</a></span> (1.16.5)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/oh-the-biomes-youll-go-fabric\">BYG</a></span> (1.16.5)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/diamold\">Diamold</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mythicmetals\">Mythic Metals</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fantasycraft-fabric/\">Fantasycraft</a></span> (1.16.5)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tungsten-mod\">Tungsten Mod</a></span> (1.16.5)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dragonloot\">DragonLoot</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/luxore\">Luxore</a></span> (1.16.5)</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pigsteel/files\">PigSteel</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gobber-fabric\">Gobber</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/adabranium\">Adabranium</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/simply-platinum/files/3208198\">Simply Platinum</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/aether/\">Aether</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/earlygame\">EarlyGame</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
